high_descs: Walk to the doorway to your right, and hang a right, then go straight and walk past the living room, then go to the bedroom in the opposite and go to the bed.
Take the dishsponge on the right side of the bed.
Go to the countertop to your left, then turn right and head towards the fridge, then go to the microwave to your right.
Put the dishsponge on the countertop in front of the microwave.
Turn around and go left to the counter and walk straight to the bedroom and go to the bed.
Take the dishsponge from the bed.
Turn right and walk straight through the door way and hang a right then head to the countertop and go to the microwave to your right.
Stack the dishsponge on top of the other dishsponge on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Stack two DishSponge on the CounterTop

high_descs: Turn right and head down the passage on the right to reach the bedroom and face the bed.
Pick up the green dishsponge from the bed.
Turn around to head out of the bedroom and turn right to reach the countertop in front of the microwave.
Put the dishsponge on the countertop.
Turn around to exit the kitchen and turn left to reach the bed.
Pick up the green dishsponge from the bed.
Turn around to exit the bedroom and walk into the kitchen on the right to reach the countertop in front of the microwave.
Put the green dishsponge on the countertop with the other dishsponge.
anns.task_desc: Put two DishSponge on the CounterTop.
